NEWSCAST - STUDIO A - 8:00 PM

Countdown clock ticking. Floor director ready.

[[AUDIO (cue 1) [source=playback, file="news_open.mp3", level=-3dB]: News open music — cued and ready]]

[[CAMERA (cue 1) [preset=anchor_wide, source=cam1]: Camera 1 — anchor wide — on standby]]

ON AIR.

