Anchor looks to camera.

AUDIO (cue 6) [source=anchor_mic, compression=medium, gate=-30dB]: Anchor microphone hot

ANCHOR (MICHAEL CHEN)
Good evening. Tonight's top stories:

A six-alarm fire in the downtown district.

GRAPHICS (cue 7) [template=over_shoulder, image="fire_still.jpg", position=OTS_right]: OTS — fire image

ANCHOR
The mayor's office responds to budget controversy.

GRAPHICS (cue 8) [template=over_shoulder, image="mayor_still.jpg", position=OTS_right]: OTS — mayor image

ANCHOR
And local students make history at the science fair.

GRAPHICS (cue 9) [template=over_shoulder, image="students_still.jpg", position=OTS_right]: OTS — students image

ANCHOR
I'm Michael Chen. This is the Evening News.

GRAPHICS (cue 10): Clear OTS graphic

ANCHOR
We begin tonight with that fire. Reporter Sandra Lee is live on scene.

CAMERA (cue 11) [source=cam2, transition=cut]: Cut to cam 2 — wide two-shot

AUDIO (cue 12) [source=IFB, level=-6dB]: IFB to anchor — reporter ready

PLAYBACK (cue 13) [file="fire_live_pkg.mp4", audio=stereo]: Roll live shot — reporter package

Reporter appears live.

GRAPHICS (cue 14) [template=lower_third, content="Sandra Lee — Live", position=lower_left, duration=8s]: Lower third — reporter name

GRAPHICS (cue 15) [template=location_bug, content="Downtown — 4th and Main", position=lower_right]: Location bug

REPORTER (SANDRA LEE) (V.O.)
Michael, the blaze began just after 6 PM...

PLAYBACK (cue 16) [file="fire_footage.mp4", duration=45s]: B-roll — fire footage

Reporter continues VO.

GRAPHICS (cue 17) on reporter tosback: Clear all graphics

CAMERA (cue 18) [source=cam1, transition=cut]: Cut to anchor — cam 1

ANCHOR
Thank you, Sandra. We'll have more on that story throughout the evening.

Moving now to the budget controversy...

GRAPHICS (cue 19) [template=full_screen, file="budget_graphic.mp4", duration=20s]: Full screen graphic — budget breakdown

